#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:1
msgid "Krita's Brush Engine options overview."
msgstr "Krita 的筆刷引擎選項概覽。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:19
msgid "Options"
msgstr "選項"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:25
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:21
msgid "Airbrush"
msgstr "噴槍"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you hold the brush still, but are still pressing down, this will keep "
"adding color onto the canvas. The lower the rate, the quicker the color gets "
"added."
msgstr ""
"勾選噴槍選項後，若按下筆刷原地不動，將會繼續在畫布上添加顏色。頻率設定越高，"
"顏色添加得越快。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:35
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:31
msgid "Mirror"
msgstr "鏡射"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:39
msgid "This allows you to mirror the Brush tip with Sensors."
msgstr "此選項可以使用感測器的數值鏡射筆尖。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:41
msgid "Horizontal"
msgstr "水平"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:42
msgid "Mirrors the mask horizontally."
msgstr "水平鏡射遮罩。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:44
msgid "Vertical"
msgstr "垂直"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:44
msgid "Mirrors the mask vertically."
msgstr "垂直鏡射遮罩。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:48
msgid ""
"Some examples of mirroring and using it in combination with :ref:"
"`option_rotation`."
msgstr "上圖是鏡射與\\ :ref:`option_rotation`\\ 合并使用的效果。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:53
msgid "Rotation"
msgstr "旋轉"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:55
msgid "This allows you to affect Angle of your brush tip with Sensors."
msgstr "可使用感測器影響筆尖的角度。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:61
msgid "In the above example, several applications of the parameter."
msgstr "在上面的例子中，參數的幾個應用。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:63
msgid ""
"Drawing Angle -- A common one, usually used in combination with rake-type "
"brushes. Especially effect because it does not rely on tablet-specific "
"sensors. Sometimes, Tilt-Direction or Rotation is used to achieve a similar-"
"more tablet focused effect, where with Tilt the 0° is at 12 o'clock, Drawing "
"angle uses 3 o'clock as 0°."
msgstr ""
"筆跡方向：這是一個比較常用的傳感測器，經常和耙式筆刷配合使用。它不需要數位板"
"就能生效。壓感筆的筆身傾斜和筆身旋轉有時候也會被用來得到類似的效果，但筆身傾"
"斜把 12 點鐘方向作為 0°，而筆跡走向把 3 點鐘方向作為 0°。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:64
msgid ""
"Fuzzy -- Also very common, this gives a nice bit of randomness for texture."
msgstr "隨機度：也很常用，這為紋理提供了一些隨機變化。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:65
msgid ""
"Distance -- With careful editing of the Sensor curve, you can create nice "
"patterns."
msgstr "距離：通過精心編輯感測器曲線，您可以創建好看的圖案。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:66
msgid "Fade -- This slowly fades the rotation from one into another."
msgstr "淡化：讓旋轉效果的過渡更加平滑。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:67
msgid ""
"Pressure -- An interesting one that can create an alternative looking line."
msgstr "壓力：可以有趣的畫出另一種風格的筆畫。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:72
msgid "Lightness Strength"
msgstr "亮度強度"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:73
msgid ""
"This allows you to affect the Lightness Strength of your brush tip with "
"Sensors. Only available with brush tips in Lightness Map mode."
msgstr "這允許您使用感測器影響筆尖的亮度強度。僅適用於亮度映射模式下的筆尖。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:78
msgid ""
"This changes the contrast of the brush tip, so that at 100%, the full effect "
"of the lightness variation is visible in the brush, while at 0% the brush "
"paints without any lightness variation.  This allows a variable impasto "
"effect with lightness brushes, and for variation in texture stamp brushes "
"that use a lightness-enabled brush tip."
msgstr ""
"此選項改變筆尖的對比度。在 100% 強度下，筆尖的整個變化範圍都得到保留，而在 0 "
"% 強度下，筆尖沒有任何亮度變化。在亮度映射模式下配合帶有紋理的筆尖使用讓筆畫"
"呈現多變的厚塗效果。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:83
msgid "Scatter"
msgstr "分散"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:85
msgid ""
"This parameter allows you to set the random placing of a brush-dab. You can "
"affect them with Sensors."
msgstr "此參數設定筆刷印跡的隨機分散程度。您可以使用感測器。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:87
msgid "X"
msgstr "X"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:88
msgid "The scattering on the angle you are drawing from."
msgstr "朝您繪畫筆跡的方向分散。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:90
msgid "Y"
msgstr "Y"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:90
msgid ""
"The scattering, perpendicular to the drawing angle (has the most effect)."
msgstr "垂直於繪製方向分散（影響最大）。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:97
msgid "Sharpness"
msgstr "銳利度"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:101
msgid ""
"Puts a threshold filter over the brush mask. This can be used for brush like "
"strokes, but it also makes for good pixel art brushes."
msgstr ""
"在筆刷遮罩之上應用的一個閾值過濾器。它既可用於類似筆觸的筆刷，也可用於像素藝"
"術筆刷。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:103
msgid "Strength"
msgstr "強度"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:104
msgid "Controls the threshold, and can be controlled by the sensors below."
msgstr "控制閾值，可由下面的感測器控制。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:106
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Softness"
msgid "Soften Edge"
msgstr "柔和度"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:106
msgid ""
"Controls the extra non-fully opaque pixels. This adds a little softness to "
"the stroke."
msgstr "控制額外的非完全不透明（半透明）像素。這為筆畫增加了一點柔和度。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:110
msgid ""
"The sensors now control the threshold instead of the subpixel precision, "
"softness slider was added."
msgstr "感測器現在控制閾值而不是子像素精度，添加了柔和度滑動條。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:116
msgid "Align the brush preview outline to the pixel grid."
msgstr ""

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:114
msgid ""
"Whether to have the brush outline align to the pixel grid. This is useful "
"with some forms of pixel art."
msgstr ""

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:121
msgid "Size"
msgstr "大小"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:125
msgid ""
"This parameter is not the diameter itself, but rather the curve for how it's "
"affected."
msgstr "這個參數不是直徑，而是調整曲線影響筆刷大小時的手感輕重和快慢。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:127
msgid ""
"So, if you want to lock the diameter of the brush, lock the Brush tip. "
"Locking the size parameter will only lock this curve. Allowing this curve to "
"be affected by the Sensors can be very useful to get the right kind of "
"brush. For example, if you have trouble drawing fine lines, try to use a "
"concave curve set to pressure. That way you'll have to press hard for thick "
"lines."
msgstr ""
"因此，如果你想要鎖定筆刷的直徑，你應該鎖定「筆尖」選項。鎖定「大小」選項只會"
"鎖定它的感測器曲線。你可以通過曲線來影響感測器的作用，打造具有某些特性的筆"
"刷。例如，如果你不擅長勾畫細線，你可以把壓力曲線設為下凹的形狀，這樣你便需要"
"更大的力量才能畫出粗線條。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:131
msgid ""
"Also popular is setting the size to the sensor fuzzy or perspective, with "
"the later in combination with a :ref:`assistant_perspective`."
msgstr ""
"大小選項還有另外兩種常見用法。一種是把它映射到隨機度，這樣可以畫出輪廓不那麼"
"均勻的線條。還有一種是把它映射到透視感測器，配合\\ :ref:"
"`assistant_perspective`\\ 輔助尺使用，可以把畫出的線條粗細也按照輔助尺來進行"
"透視繪圖。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:138
msgid "Softness"
msgstr "柔和度"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:140
msgid "This allows you to affect Fade with Sensors."
msgstr "這允許您使用感測器影響淡化程度。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:144
msgid ""
"Has a slight brush-decreasing effect, especially noticeable with soft-brush, "
"and is overall more noticeable on large brushes."
msgstr "它會讓筆刷看起來輕微的變小了。越柔和越大的筆刷，效果就越明顯。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:149
msgid "Source"
msgstr "來源"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:151
msgid "Picks the source-color for the brush-dab."
msgstr "為筆刷印跡選擇源顏色。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:153
msgid "Plain Color"
msgstr "純色"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:154
msgid "Current foreground color."
msgstr "使用當前的前景色。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:155
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:187
msgid "Gradient"
msgstr "漸變"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:156
msgid "Picks active gradient."
msgstr "選取當前的漸變。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:157
msgid "Uniform Random"
msgstr "筆尖隨機"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:158
msgid "Gives a random color to each brush dab."
msgstr "為每個筆刷印跡賦予隨機顏色。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:159
msgid "Total Random"
msgstr "筆畫隨機"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:160
msgid "Random noise pattern is now painted."
msgstr "隨機噪點模式。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:161
msgid "Pattern"
msgstr "圖案"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:162
msgid "Uses active pattern, but alignment is different per stroke."
msgstr "使用當前的圖案，但圖案的對齊每筆不同。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:164
msgid "Locked Pattern"
msgstr "筆尖鎖定圖案"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:164
msgid "Locks the pattern to the brushdab."
msgstr "將圖案鎖定到筆刷印跡。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:169
msgid "Mix"
msgstr "混合"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:171
msgid ""
"Allows you to affect the mix of the :ref:`option_source` color with Sensors. "
"It will work with Plain Color and Gradient as source. If Plain Color is "
"selected as source, it will mix between the currently selected foreground "
"and background color. If Gradient is selected, it chooses a point on the "
"gradient to use as painting color according to the sensors selected."
msgstr ""
"此項用來調整感測器對\\ :ref:`option_source`\\ 選項的混合效果。它可以在純色和"
"漸變兩種顏色來源下工作。如果顏色來源為純色，它將在當前選擇的前景色和背景色之"
"間混合。如果顏色來源是漸變，則會根據感測器所選的漸變對應顏色。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:176
msgid "Uses"
msgstr "使用範例"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:182
msgid "Flow map"
msgstr "流向貼圖"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:181
msgid ""
"The above example uses a :program:`Krita` painted flowmap in the 3D program :"
"program:`Blender`. A brush was set to :menuselection:`Source --> Gradient` "
"and :menuselection:`Mix --> Drawing angle`. The gradient in question "
"contained the 360° for normal map colors. Flow maps are used in several "
"Shaders, such as brushed metal, hair and certain river-shaders."
msgstr ""
"上圖左側是 :program:`Krita` 繪制的流向貼圖，右邊是該貼圖在 3D 程式 :program:"
"`Blender` 中的效果。筆刷選項為 :menuselection:`來源 --> 漸變` 和 :"
"menuselection:`混合 --> 筆跡方向`。此處的漸變包含了 360° 的法線貼圖顏色。一些"
"著色器需要使用流向貼圖來表現拉絲金屬、頭髮和流水效果。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:189
msgid ""
"Exactly the same as using :menuselection:`Source --> Gradient` with :"
"guilabel:`Mix`, but only available for the Color Smudge Brush."
msgstr ""
"效果與 :menuselection:`來源 --> 漸變` 配合 :guilabel:`混合` 使用時一樣，但只"
"在顏色塗抹筆刷下可用。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:193
msgid "You can either:"
msgstr "您可以："

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:195
msgid ""
"Leave the default :menuselection:`Foreground --> Background gradient` "
"setting, and just change the foreground and background colors"
msgstr ""
"使用預設的 :menuselection:`（前景到背景色）漸變` 設定，然後只更改漸變中的前景"
"色和背景色"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:196
msgid "Select a more specific gradient"
msgstr "選擇更具體的漸變"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:197
msgid "Or make custom gradients."
msgstr "或製作自定義漸變。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:203
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:199
msgid "Spacing"
msgstr "間距"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:207
msgid "This allows you to affect :ref:`option_brush_tip` with :ref:`sensors`."
msgstr ""
"這選項可使用\\ :ref:`sensors`\\ 調整\\ :ref:`option_brush_tip`\\ 的間距。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:212
msgid "Isotropic spacing"
msgstr "各向同性間距"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:212
msgid ""
"Instead of the spacing being related to the ratio of the brush, it will be "
"on diameter only."
msgstr "計算間距時不考慮筆刷的長寬比，只考慮筆刷的直徑。"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:220
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:216
msgid "Ratio"
msgstr "長寬比"

#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_settings/options.rst:222
msgid ""
"Allows you to change the ratio of the brush and bind it to parameters. This "
"also works for predefined brushes."
msgstr "允許您更改筆刷的比例並將其綁定到參數。這也適用於預定義的筆刷。"
